{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1729654053.89885", "card_id": "Q_1723717320", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 237}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待华为 10 月 22 日正式亮相的 nova13 系列？有哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "今天，华为 nova13 系列正式亮相，华为官方公布了别具一格的外观设计及支持 AI 修图等诸多功能。 对于此次华为 nova13 的亮相，有哪些信息值得关注？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-c25d7f8a8b833da29493040f87319c4e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "361 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/1723717320"}}, "attached_info": "CkEI796Bx4GLxeoxEAMaCTExMTMyMTM4NSCznN64BjAAOJsCQAByCjE3MjM3MTczMjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1729654053.90880", "card_id": "Q_265492555", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 94}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "像兔子这样柔顺无攻击力还独居智商低的动物是怎样能在地球上存活这么多年的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "看蜡笔小新突然看到一集关于小兔子的，就突然想到这个问题。 以前家里也养过兔子，就一直在吃吃吃，后来学校做实验也接触过兔子，温顺得谁抱都可以呀。 查了一些资料发现兔子还是独居，那么就想问，兔子这样温顺无攻击力的动物怎么存活这么久的？只是因为跑得快会打洞吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d21bf80086af149ae8715304c1337c4f_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "221 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/265492555"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I796Bx4GLxeoxEAMaCDIwNjI4NjE3IMfM4tIFMAA4iwFAAXIJMjY1NDkyNTU1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1729654053.91481", "card_id": "Q_36091285", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46d